What is read_data.fetch_data(file_name, batch_size) ?
Does it return an operation?
Overwriting the operation with the data in the next step looks bad, but shouldn't result in an error.
You should probably take a look at https://www.tensorflow.org/programmers_guide/datasets

body:
What is `read_data.fetch_data(file_name, batch_size)` ?
Does it return an operation?
Overwriting the operation with the data in the next step looks bad, but shouldn't result in an error.
You should probably take a look at https://www.tensorflow.org/programmers_guide/datasets
